This query searches for multi-factor authentication (MFA) helps protect devices and data 
 that are accessible to these users. Adding more authentication methods, increases the level of protection 
 if one factor is compromised. This hunting query depends on SenservaPro data connector (SenservaPro_CL Parser or Table)

This query searches for an service principal is not using a client certificate or secret is not secure. 
 It is recommended that you review your needs and use an Authentication method 
 for sign-in. This hunting query depends on SenservaPro data connector (SenservaPro_CL Parser or Table)
